parameters: \n<\N[5]>\F[62]So, it was you after all... Kino.

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]I wanted to talk to you without Sawa
around. Huh? Don't give me that scary
look and be on guard.

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F]Before we start talking, could you please lock
the door to that hallway? Just in case.

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]If that caution had been displayed from
the beginning, we might not have ended
up in this situation, huh?

\n<\N[5]>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[F](Indeed... I have no words to retort on that
point)

\n<Kino>\F[62]\FF[91]\AA[FF]Well, fine. But... I'll make sure you can't
escape while I'm not here, okay?

\n<\N[5]>\F[61](Even if you go through the trouble of moving
to the bed, there's no way you can
escape...)

\F[61]When I moved to the bed... I remembered the
time when Kino helped me and
accidentally touched her skin.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61](It was soft... and it had a nice scent
too...)

\F[61]My crotch is throbbing... but I suppose
that can't be helped. Kino, who claims
to be in charge of visuals, has a baby
face but a well-proportioned and
beautiful face when seen from the side.
She's quite the beauty.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61](Originally, she was just a underground idol... but
I discovered a strange charisma in her
that was different from Neon, so I
scouted her.)

\n<\N[5]>\F[61](We had a big argument back then... You
were adamant about not betraying our
comrades.)

\F[61]In the end, Kino was persuaded by our
comrades and ended up joining the
members. And even now, I know that she
still keeps in touch with our old
comrades.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61](Of course he'd be angry... He's someone
who cares about his comrades more than
anyone else.)
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...Well then, shall we begin?

\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]The sound of the lock being closed behind
me echoes in the room. A shiver runs
down my spine... That's right, this is
it.

In contrast to the overwhelming
performance and beauty that attracts
everyone, Minato possesses a captivating
charisma, but hers...

A unique sense of fear that is not
befitting of her baby face. It makes
others instinctively bow down and feel
relieved. Her charismatic dominance. She
possessed that... It's only now, in a
time like this, that I finally
understand.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I don't have any intention of prying into
your and Sawa's affairs. That's a matter
between the two of you, and it's not an
issue for an outsider like me to
interfere in.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]However, that is... a story for after settling
the score. I will make you pay for the
sin of making Sawa cry right here and
now.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Sin? What right does a traitor like you have
to speak...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Ah, that's why... This is also my
atonement.
\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Kino slowly approaches as she says that.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F](What... What are you planning to do to me?
D-Don't tell me you're going to kill

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Don't be so cautious... I just have something
to talk about.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]...Talk? What, did you finally feel like helping
out?

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...Hmm, I suppose it's fine to side with you.
However, there are conditions.
\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Conditions? Well, let's hear them for now...

\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Kino straightened their posture and looked
straight into my eyes.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...What is the important secret that \N[5]-san
holds? Presenting that information is a
condition.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]...Isn't that a bit one-sided? Sorry, but I
can't easily talk about it.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Well, I suppose that's true... There is a
possibility that I might snitch.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]No, I trust you on that. I know Kino isn't
the kind of person to do something like
that.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]W-What's with that... If that's the case, then
why...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]There's one thing I want to ask Kino. If you
answer honestly, I'll reveal the
information.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...Is it really okay with something like
that? If it's just that much...

\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]This time, I straightened my posture and
looked straight into Kino's eyes.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]...The question is simple. What is the real
reason for Kino siding with Udo?

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...D-Didn't I already say that? It's because they
have data of me engaging in activities
with them...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Certainly, that might be one reason. But didn't
you phrase it in a way that implies
there is another reason?

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]There might be a clue to finding a solution
by talking, and if Kino wishes for it, I
will absolutely not disclose it.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Kino... I still intend to be your manager. If
there's something you can't solve on
your own... please rely on me.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...Will you absolutely not tell anyone...?
\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]I absolutely won't tell anyone.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]From someone else's perspective, it's really
a trivial matter... but you won't laugh,
right...?

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]I won't laugh, and there's no such thing
as something trivial...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I see... That's right. You're that kind
of person...

\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Kino bowed their head and fell silent. After
a moment of deep thought, they finally
opened their mouth.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]It's the first time... for me...
\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]For the first time... what is it?

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]So, I came for the first time! With Udo...
during sex!

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]...Um... Was there never anything before that?
That...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Well... I've had some light orgasms before. But
that kind of climax experience was the
first time for me...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I've never felt satisfied even when I did it
alone... I always thought there was
something wrong with my body...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]I see... So you became dependent on your
sexual activities with Udo... is that
what happened?
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Yeah... To put it simply...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F](Is it a mental issue...? It seems like
there's no problem with their body...)

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]You must be disgusted, right? Betraying
Minato for such a reason... I'm truly
pathetic... And I feel sorry for
everyone too...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]No, everyone has their own worries... Even
if it may seem trivial to others, it can
be a heavy burden for the person
themselves.

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]It was tough... I'm sorry for not
noticing...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]\N[5]-san, you didn't do anything wrong... Ugh,
ughhh...

Kino covered their face with both hands and
broke down crying. Unable to find the
right words to say, I could only stay
silent and wait for them to stop
crying...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Haah... I cried, I cried... It's been so many
years since I last cried...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]I regret not having a camera. It was a
once-in-a- lifetime chance to hold onto
a weakness of yours...

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]This stubborn and despicable small-dicked
bastard...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Stop with the small-dick comments... It
hurts boys, you know...
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Hahaha... However, what a waste I've done.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I missed the first and last chance to
corrupt Kino- chan, you know? If I had
gently embraced them or something, they
would have easily fallen...
\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Seriously... Kino-chan is so easy.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]I'm not that easy! Well... that aside.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...I can't understand something.

\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Not only did they expose my secret, but
they also showed my crying face...

\n<\N[5]>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[F]Hey, don't say things that sound bad. I
didn't really expose anything, you know.
\n<Kino>\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]...It's okay to keep this a secret, right?
\F[61]\FF[95]\AA[FF]Kino stands up with an enchanting smile.
